Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:05.48,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Vamos viajar por todos os mares do mundo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:07.85,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,levantando nosso grito de guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:12.19,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se você já se decidiu, deixe o sinal de partida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.63,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:25.34,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos escapar do curso definido
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:28.77,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,ao longo da fronteira entre o céu e o mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:34.15,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Agora estamos remando em nosso caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:40.55,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,para uma aventura escondida no fundo escuro do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:47.49,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Não parece divertido só de pensar nisso?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:51.96,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vamos viajar por todos os mares do mundo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.23,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,levantando nosso grito de guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.57,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se você já se decidiu, deixe o sinal para a partida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:01.01,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:11.58,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Aquela sensação que tivemos quando zarpamos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:15.05,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,é algo que nunca esquecerei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:16.72,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Por causa disso
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:20.53,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,nada vai me assustar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.77,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Agora, conforme a viagem se aproxima, nossos batimentos cardíacos acelerados
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:33.84,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,gravam um ritmo de aventura em nossos corações tímidos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:38.11,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Pegue todos os tesouros
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.41,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,enquanto ri alto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:44.85,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Então distribua tudo em uma grande festa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:47.35,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,fazendo barulho...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.50,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,A vida é uma aventura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:51.00,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Fica ligado, que é perigosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.50,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Quem será um de nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.50,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,E a viagem segue porque
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.00,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Somos os piratas do povo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.80,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Para o oeste! Para o leste!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:00.30,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vou traçar minha rota e navegar até o One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.60,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Encha seu coração vazio com sonhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.91,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Abra suas asas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:11.31,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se você colorir seu coração com o vento soprando
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.65,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,você seguirá em frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:17.72,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Pegue todos os tesouros
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:20.09,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(60,0)}enquanto ri alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:24.49,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,então distribua tudo em uma grande festa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.23,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,fazendo barulho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}A gigante batalha contra o Zumbi 900!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.30,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Eles não têm um cartaz de procurado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.77,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,O que significa que os que sobraram são...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.74,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Aquele chapéu de palha de antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.98,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Uma mulher laranja...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.45,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,E um herói legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.88,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Estou esquecendo de três pessoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.60,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Onde elas podem estar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:00.86,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Ela acordou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.05,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.09,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Eu odeio baratas! Tire-as daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.85,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Baratas não!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.94,Secondary,zombie,0,0,0,,Perona-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:03.95,Secondary,zombie,0,0,0,,Perona-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.63,Secondary,zombie,0,0,0,,Por favor, acalme-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.85,Secondary,zombie,0,0,0,,Não existe tal coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.28,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Onde estou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.30,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,O inimigo não está mais aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:17.07,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Você estava inconsciente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.63,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.55,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,E para você, de todas as pessoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.02,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com a mansão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.34,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Isso foi obra dos piratas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.22,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Os piratas causaram muitos problemas, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:32.11,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Esses são os vestígios da fúria irracional de Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.02,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Oars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:38.85,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,E, de acordo com nossos relatórios, Oars aniquilou todos os Generais Zumbis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.20,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,O exército supremo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.43,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Oars está fora de controle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.22,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Bem, isso é-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:51.90,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.84,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Irmãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.29,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Mulher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.75,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,O-Oars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:03.57,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,A-A propósito, parece que Hogback-sama foi pisoteado...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.49,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:07.10,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Nenhuma mulher aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.76,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Mulher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.29,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Mulher?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.63,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim, eu tenho que sair daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:17.50,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Thriller Bark está sendo destruído por Oars e os piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:21.13,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Rápido! Reúnam as provisões e os tesouros!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.80,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Depois que você os colocar no navio pirata, nós vamos embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.58,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Deles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.36,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.90,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Nós escaparemos no navio deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:28.56,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.62,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Sim, imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.85,Captions,Sign,0,0,210,,{\fad(600,0)}Enquanto isso, em uma sala vazia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.72,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Agora, o beijo do voto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:44.63,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.23,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,E-E-E-Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.03,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.33,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Não! Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.05,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Você acordou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.25,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Desista, então!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:56.70,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Quando eu te beijar, você se tornará minha esposa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.54,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eu disse não! Sua besta invisível e pervertida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:02.30,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eu ainda quero viver aventuras!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.27,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Fique quieta e aceite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.35,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Você se tornará a esposa do Rei do Cemitério! A Rainha do Cemitério!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.84,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Não! O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.44,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Maldito seja, Namizou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.98,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lo-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.10,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.45,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Namizou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.37,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Você!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:29.91,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Como você pôde me trair?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:35.21,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Aquele discurso naquela época sobre me apoiar não passou de uma mentira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:39.29,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Que apoio?! Você estava tentando roubar Ab-sama de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.15,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Que tipo de amiga você é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.34,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,E-Espere um minuto, Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.35,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eu estava inconsciente esse tempo todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.92,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eu não sei o que-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.44,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Um vestido de noiva?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:50.50,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Por que estou usando isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:51.28,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,É lindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.55,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Não é lindo, sua traidora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.90,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Espere! Isso é um mal-entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.79,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Droga, Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:02.64,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Você não só interrompeu meu casamento, mas está tentando machucar minha noiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.06,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Cale a boca e case comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.93,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Claro que não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:10.16,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Ab-sama, você não tem ideia, tem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.66,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,O nome verdadeiro dessa mulher é Namizou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.84,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,E ela é na verdade um homem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.39,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.80,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Isso é impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.63,Thoughts,Nami,0,0,0,,Eu disse isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.47,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Mas, no banheiro eu certamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.82,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Desapareça, Namizou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.44,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Pare, Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.36,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Ei, pare já, Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.48,Thoughts,Nami,0,0,0,,Ela está errando...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.30,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Namizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:47.93,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.66,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Fuja, Namizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.47,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Eu o manterei ocupado.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.71,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Estou aqui para te salvar, minha amiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.56,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.23,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Ab-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:06.54,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Agora que você sabe a verdade, Absalom, esqueça-a e case-se comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.03,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.64,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Minha noiva está fugindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.15,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Eu sou sua noiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.96,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Não há dúvidas de que ela é uma mulher, Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.29,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Saia do meu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.61,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.54,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Zumbi intrometida...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:42.14,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Você me fez desperdiçar minha força.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.22,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Muito inteligente...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.75,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Você parou de correr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:58.07,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.57,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Você não pode fugir de mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.45,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,Eu sou um homem invisível.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.05,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sandā Chāji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.77,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Como ousa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.44,Flashbacks,Lola,0,0,0,,Estou aqui para te salvar, minha amiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.34,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Como ousa machucar Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:30.12,Main,Absalom,0,0,0,,É isso! Venha direto para os meus braços!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.82,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Suingu Āmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.60,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Não vai te machucar de qualquer maneira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.62,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Estou ciente disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.47,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Como assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.05,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Antes ele não tinha sentido nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:04.61,Thoughts,zombie,0,0,0,,Como imaginei! Ele já se esforçou quando lutou contra aquele homem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.12,Thoughts,zombie,0,0,0,,Deve ser isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.04,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Bem, não importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.32,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eu ganhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Devo ter tocado em um ponto fraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:16.96,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.22,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.19,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Aguente firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Obrigada por vir me salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.94,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Por que você está me agradecendo, Namizou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.36,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Somos amigas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.78,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Mas... Naquela época, eu tinha medo de você, então menti...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.42,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Me desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Na verdade, sou uma mulher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.89,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Você é boba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.89,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Eu sabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.97,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Mais importante! Ab-sama está desprevenido agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.20,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Você será meu marido agora, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.89,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Você está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:12.02,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Saia, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.67,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Mulher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.59,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Herói maneiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.30,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Qual era o nome dele?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.74,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.74,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza de que era Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Não, você entendeu errado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Terminava com... "rs".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:27.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.66,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Uau, esse é um palpite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Uars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ainda falta alguma coisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.39,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.74,Main,All,0,0,0,,É isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:42.19,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Com licença... Sinto muito, mas meu corpo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.51,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Sim, não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.16,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Você ainda consegue se mover?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:46.95,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.33,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Então saia da frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.02,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Ei, Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.34,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Se você tem a sombra do Luffy dentro de você...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.63,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Então você já devia saber que nunca deve...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:06.36,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,subestimar a força dos seus companheiros de tripulação.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:19.51,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Vocês são um bando resistente, pequenos piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:33.45,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Tenho uma proposta para todos vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Que tal virarmos esse cara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.84,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Isso certamente seria legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,E-Espere um minuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,V-Virar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.91,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Essa coisa enorme?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:54.59,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,No entanto, com esse tamanho enorme, os ataques de Luffy são mais impressionantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.83,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Mas ele não parece nem um pouco um "Rei Pirata".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Como atacaremos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.30,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Existem inúmeras maneiras de fazer isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.04,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Ele deve ter uma fraqueza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:11.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Quando você está pegando um peixe grande, a tática mais comum é enfraquecê-lo aos poucos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.29,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Se esse é o plano, então eu estou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.45,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Muito assustado.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.45,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Eu vou te esmagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.30,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Aí vem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.52,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.10,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Batida de bunda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.39,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Que tipo de ataque é esse!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.22,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Se espalhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.80,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ōgama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.16,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Bastardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:45.41,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, eu vou te mostrar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.26,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Nosso poder combinado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.21,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Vocês dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.50,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.27,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Tática Quinze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.27,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.22,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.16,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Vamos usar "isso" aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.20,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:01.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.66,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Fiquem atentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.65,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Só segure minhas pernas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.53,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,O que ele está aprontando?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.06,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Aqui vamos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.66,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Piratas atracando 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Guerreiro robô gigante...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:29.84,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Grande Imperador!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.09,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Espera um minuto, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.23,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,O braço esquerdo ainda não encaixou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.40,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.50,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Ei, o que você está esperando, Nico Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.86,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Apresse-se e atraque no meu braço esquerdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.34,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Robin, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Venha, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.67,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Faça como eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.09,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Para uma pessoa, isso é vergonhoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.48,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Por que você parou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.64,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Por que você também está chocado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.29,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Eu estava começando a ficar animado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.10,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Faça!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.68,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,A atracação!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:14.77,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Que absurdo! Não acredito que me fizeram fazer uma coisa dessas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.93,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Não, esqueça o que aconteceu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:22.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Robin, se você tivesse se juntado, teríamos completado o Guerreiro Robô, Grande Imperador!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.53,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Eu nunca pensei que você nos trairia! Nunca!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Luffy teria feito isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.20,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Nunca mais me peça...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.42,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,para fazer isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:38.66,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hora da vingança, seu bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.02,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.53,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Vou pegar emprestado essa coisa enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:48.37,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Você! Esse é meu Nunchaku Pesado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Não tem jeito,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.72,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Vou te emprestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.31,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Seu bastardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:58.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Tenho que me apressar e ir resgatar Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.06,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Você?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.95,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:13.31,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Quando eu chegar no braço esquerdo dele, você cuida da articulação!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.86,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.51,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.09,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,A geladeira já está cheia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.88,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Nada mais vai caber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:34.05,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Ainda tem a despensa, não tem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:34.84,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.27,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Depressa com o tesouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.58,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Carregue o resto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.64,Main,Zombies,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.19,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Pegue isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.62,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tokuyō Abura Boshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\pos(555,702)}Tri
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\pos(605,702)}plo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\pos(697,702)}Tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.87,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Ei, sobrancelha encaracolada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.66,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Me jogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Carregando uma coisa tão grande...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.51,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Está tudo bem se você não consegue lidar com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.93,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.31,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Claro que posso, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.98,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Arume do Rēru... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.82,Main,Sanji,0, 0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pawā Shūto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.70,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Great Sword Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0: 16:23.56,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Cien Fleur...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.07,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Biggu Tsurīlit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.10,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,O-O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.73,Main,Oz ,0,0,0,,P-Perigoso... Estou caindo! Estou caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.38,Main,Franky,0,0,0, ,Veja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:48.02,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Minhas escadas super instantâneas no ar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:53.82,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Furankī Sukaiuōku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.96,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Mas... esse ponto de apoio não vai durar muito mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.14,Main,Franky,0,0 ,0,,Vamos logo, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.07,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:08.19,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Supā...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0: 17:10.66,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Furappā...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:11.57,Main,Both,0,0, 0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gongu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:21.12,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Independentemente do tamanho, o corpo humano sempre tem os mesmos pontos fracos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.59,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Bater no seu queixo vai sacudir um pouco seu cérebro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.43,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Agora seu único apoio é aquela perna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.55,Main,Sanji,0,0,0 ,,Monstro Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.32,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Anchimanā ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.84,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kikku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.45,Main,Sanji,0, 0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kōsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.65,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Virou completamente aquele monstro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.55,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Tudo bem! Caia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.26,Main, Sanji,0,0,0,,Um a menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:11.34,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Ei, ei! Isso não parece um mansão mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.96,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,O que são esses movimentos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.04,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Acrobacia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.98,Main,zombie, 0,0,0,,S-Será que...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.44,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Alguém o virou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.78,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, use a cabeça.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:26.47,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Nem mesmo um exército de mil homens seria capaz de tal coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:37.29,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Eu vou ficar bem, Namizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.62,Main,Lola,0, 0,0,,Você vai em frente e escapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.37,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Deixe-me explicar a situação atual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.83,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lola...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.88,Main,Lola ,0,0,0,,Aquele seu amigo, Luffy Chapéu de Palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:52.09,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,O Zumbi Especial que segura sua sombra está devastando toda a ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.37,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,É o zumbi que vimos naquela sala de congelados.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:58.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Que problemático!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:01.36,Main,Nami, 0,0,0,,Como vamos tirar a sombra do Luffy daquele monstro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:02.64,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Mas... .
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:07.06,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Não tem como eu voltar de mãos vazias depois de passar por esse pesadelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.52,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Aí está!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.56,Main,Nami ,0,0,0,,E não está trancado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:29.81,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Por que, seus bastardos...
Dialogue: 0 ,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.18,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Já estou farto de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:38.42,Main, Oz,0,0,0,,Eu vou esmagar todos vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:47.07,Thoughts,Pelona,0,0,0,,Eu só segui Moriah-sama por diversão de qualquer forma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:50.90,Thoughts,Pelona,0,0,0,,Claro que não vou ficar por aqui se minha vida estiver em jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.85,Main,Pelona ,0,0,0,,Agora, apressem-se todos vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.24,Main,Pelona,0,0,0,,Precisamos sair daqui o mais breve possível!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.98,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:03.18,Main,zombie,0 ,0,0,,Tudo bem! Carregue as provisões restantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.77,Main,Bunny,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.22,Main,Bunny,0,0,0,,Você não é um zumbi, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.82,Main,Bunny,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.54,Main,Bunny,0,0,0,,Um corpo tão grande...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:18.43,Main,Bunny,0,0,0,,Você parece um urso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.76,Main,Kuma,0,0,0,,Um urso, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.17,Main,Kuma,0,0,0,,Essa é a resposta certa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.23,Main,Kuma,0,0,0,,Moriah está...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.64,Main,Kuma,0,0,0,,por aqui?